Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:58.86,dive ed,,0,0,0,,tsuyoku mae o muite arukou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:05.06,dive ed,,0,0,0,,bokutachi wa sou mikansei dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:10.28,dive ed,,0,0,0,,sora takaku nobasu te no naka ni
